<font color=#FFFF00><i>[Episode 21]</i></font>

3
00:00:10,972 --> 00:00:11,772
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa kau?</font>

4
00:00:29,990 --> 00:00:32,730
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku pikir Seja Jeoha akan dikurung.</i></font>

5
00:00:32,760 --> 00:00:34,030
<font color=#FFFF00><i>[Raja telah memerintahkannya untuk tidak
pergi ke luar daerah yang ditentukan.]</i></font>

6
00:01:10,470 --> 00:01:11,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Seja Jeoha.</font>

7
00:01:17,970 --> 00:01:19,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Terdengar aneh...</font>

8
00:01:20,440 --> 00:01:21,980
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau memanggil seperti itu.</font>

9
00:01:29,820 --> 00:01:31,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu sepertinya baju Lin.</font>

10
00:01:33,460 --> 00:01:34,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Ah,</font>

11
00:01:35,390 --> 00:01:37,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia memberikan padaku
agar bisa kabur.</font>

12
00:01:38,190 --> 00:01:39,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku dengar Lin sudah tahu...</font>

13
00:01:40,960 --> 00:01:42,130
<font color=#FFFF00>...identitasmu sebelum aku.</font>

14
00:01:45,700 --> 00:01:46,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

15
00:01:47,900 --> 00:01:49,240
<font color=#FFFF00>Kapan kau tahu...</font>

16
00:01:51,870 --> 00:01:53,340
<font color=#FFFF00>...siapa aku?</font>

17
00:01:56,050 --> 00:01:57,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat kau datang...</font>

18
00:01:58,580 --> 00:02:02,150
<font color=#FFFF00>...ke rumahku pada hari aku menerima
hadiah pernikahan.</font>

19
00:02:07,390 --> 00:02:10,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan menghentikan pernikahan ini.</font>

20
00:02:12,730 --> 00:02:15,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Wanita yang mengenakan cadar...</font>

21
00:02:17,930 --> 00:02:19,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu aku.</font>

22
00:02:19,670 --> 00:02:22,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau juga wanita yang
diundang Apamama dan Wang Jeon?</font>

23
00:02:25,010 --> 00:02:26,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

24
00:02:28,410 --> 00:02:29,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pasti sudah melihat semuanya.</font>

25
00:02:31,710 --> 00:02:34,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau melihat aku berlutut
dan dipermalukan.</font>

26
00:02:35,950 --> 00:02:37,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Iya.</font>

27
00:02:37,320 --> 00:02:39,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun kau tetap disisiku.</font>

28
00:02:41,590 --> 00:02:42,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan...</font>

29
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:46,200
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau memberiku kalung,</font>

30
00:02:47,860 --> 00:02:49,700
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan menaruh es di lukaku.</font>

31
00:02:53,500 --> 00:02:54,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa kau tidak merasa bersalah?</font>

32
00:02:59,640 --> 00:03:01,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan kau memintaku...</font>

33
00:03:06,150 --> 00:03:08,520
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk tidak memilihmu sebagai istri.</font>

34
00:03:11,790 --> 00:03:13,160
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku.</font>

35
00:03:14,590 --> 00:03:15,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau minta maaf?</font>

36
00:03:21,900 --> 00:03:24,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Aneh sekali mendengar kau
berbicara seperti itu.</font>

37
00:03:37,280 --> 00:03:38,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pernah kesini...</font>

38
00:03:39,650 --> 00:03:41,120
<font color=#FFFF00>...saat Lin dipenjara.</font>

39
00:03:43,550 --> 00:03:45,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami duduk di sini dan bicara tentangmu.</font>

40
00:04:00,070 --> 00:04:01,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Duduklah di sampingku.</font>

41
00:04:08,180 --> 00:04:09,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa?</font>

42
00:04:11,150 --> 00:04:13,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak seharusnya duduk disitu.</font>

43
00:04:14,780 --> 00:04:16,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa karena aku Seja?</font>

44
00:04:17,150 --> 00:04:19,260
<font color=#FFFF00>...atau karena aku akan
menikah dengan wanita lain?</font>

45
00:04:23,190 --> 00:04:24,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau kenapa?</font>

46
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:28,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Mengapa kau memintaku untuk tidak
memilihmu sebagai istri?</font>

47
00:04:36,340 --> 00:04:38,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa karena ada
orang lain dalam pikiranmu?</font>

48
00:04:44,310 --> 00:04:45,780
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah tahu,</font>

49
00:04:47,520 --> 00:04:52,260
<font color=#FFFF00>...agar Tuan Muda Lin tetap disini,
Nona Dan harus menjadi istrimu.</font>

50
00:04:53,090 --> 00:04:54,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Bahkan jika kau dikirim ke Yuan?</font>

51
00:04:55,860 --> 00:04:58,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akhirnya akan pergi dan...</font>

52
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:02,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu apa yang akan terjadi
di sana?</font>

53
00:05:03,630 --> 00:05:06,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau akan menjadi istri ke 5 atau 6
seorang pejabat tua.</font>

54
00:05:06,740 --> 00:05:08,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa itu yang kau mau?
Kau sanggup melakukan itu?</font>

55
00:05:11,340 --> 00:05:12,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku...</font>

56
00:05:12,540 --> 00:05:14,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak bisa membiarkan ini.</font>

57
00:05:19,420 --> 00:05:21,150
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku khawatir dengan Ayahku.</font>

58
00:05:22,620 --> 00:05:24,220
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau mendengar kabar tentangnya...</font>

59
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:28,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan mencoba mencari tahu.</font>

60
00:05:30,630 --> 00:05:32,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisakah aku meminta
kau menjaga Ayahku?</font>

61
00:05:33,630 --> 00:05:35,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan mengurusnya.</font>

62
00:05:35,330 --> 00:05:37,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Tuan Lin bertarung dengan...</font>

63
00:05:37,100 --> 00:05:40,400
<font color=#FFFF00>...tentara Raja karenaku.
Jadi...</font>

64
00:05:40,540 --> 00:05:42,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan mengurusnya.</font>

65
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:45,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa lagi?</font>

66
00:05:47,340 --> 00:05:49,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ada lagi yang harus kulakukan
untuk Han Chun?</font>

67
00:05:55,690 --> 00:05:57,390
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau bertemu dengannya,</font>

68
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:03,390
<font color=#FFFF00>...katakan padanya So Ah
sangat berterima kasih.</font>

69
00:06:05,160 --> 00:06:06,630
<font color=#FFFF00>Tanpa sepengetahuanku,</font>

70
00:06:07,860 --> 00:06:10,030
<font color=#FFFF00>...dia melakukan banyak hal untukku.</font>

71
00:06:11,470 --> 00:06:13,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku baru tahu.</font>

72
00:06:15,140 --> 00:06:17,170
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia selalu ada untuk melindungiku.</font>

73
00:06:19,810 --> 00:06:21,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku baru tahu.</font>

74
00:06:24,250 --> 00:06:25,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Dan...</font>

75
00:06:27,850 --> 00:06:31,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Katakan padanya untuk bersikap baik
dengan orang tuanya, mencintainya,</font>

76
00:06:33,260 --> 00:06:35,290
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan berdamai.</font>

77
00:06:36,360 --> 00:06:37,890
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong katakan itu.</font>

78
00:06:42,770 --> 00:06:44,130
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak akan memberitahunya.</font>

79
00:06:49,870 --> 00:06:51,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha.</font>

80
00:06:52,380 --> 00:06:53,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan fokus pada satu hal.</font>

81
00:06:54,510 --> 00:06:56,780
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana cara kembali ke wanita itu.</font>

82
00:06:58,750 --> 00:07:00,920
<font color=#FFFF00>Kembali ke wanita yang aku kenal,</font>

83
00:07:02,290 --> 00:07:03,520
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan katakan sendiri padanya.</font>

84
00:07:05,660 --> 00:07:07,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan menangani sisanya.</font>

85
00:07:32,220 --> 00:07:34,750
<font color=#FFFF00>Dimana Seja Jeoha?/
Dia baru saja pergi.</font>

86
00:07:34,750 --> 00:07:37,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Kemana?/
Kesana.</font>

87
00:08:05,210 --> 00:08:06,320
<font color=#FFFF00>Menteri Keuangan?</font>

88
00:08:06,320 --> 00:08:08,380
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tidak dibawa ke
gedung pemerintah.</font>

89
00:08:10,820 --> 00:08:12,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada yang melihat dia dibawa
ke rumah pribadi.</font>

90
00:08:13,490 --> 00:08:16,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia seorang pedagang
dan mengenal Tuan Eun.</font>

91
00:08:16,630 --> 00:08:17,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Rumah yang mana?</font>

92
00:08:17,730 --> 00:08:19,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Itulah yang lucu.</font>

93
00:08:20,400 --> 00:08:22,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Tepat di belakang Chiwollu.</font>

94
00:08:23,500 --> 00:08:25,440
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada dua pintu masuk yang terpisah,</font>

95
00:08:26,200 --> 00:08:28,400
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi rumah-rumah itu sejajar.</font>

96
00:08:30,610 --> 00:08:32,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Cari tahu siapa pemiliknya./ Ya.</font>

97
00:08:32,740 --> 00:08:34,180
<font color=#FFFF00>Walaupun aku harus kesana.</font>

98
00:08:34,180 --> 00:08:35,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan mencari tahu.</font>

99
00:08:37,510 --> 00:08:40,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tidak ditangkap
secara resmi,</font>

100
00:08:40,080 --> 00:08:41,650
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan dibawa ke rumah pribadi.</font>

101
00:08:43,120 --> 00:08:45,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Orang itu pasti sangat percaya diri.</font>

102
00:08:45,120 --> 00:08:46,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Jeoha!</font>

103
00:08:48,260 --> 00:08:49,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang dilakukan Ratu?</font>

104
00:08:50,130 --> 00:08:53,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Ratu baru saja pergi ke kamar Raja.</font>

105
00:08:58,270 --> 00:09:01,700
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Dia sangat bersikeras sehingga tidak
ada yang bisa menghentikannya.</i></font>

106
00:09:02,410 --> 00:09:04,370
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ratu tiba.</i></font>

107
00:09:21,590 --> 00:09:23,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Sikapmu semakin buruk saat bertambah tua.</font>

108
00:09:23,790 --> 00:09:25,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Masuk begitu saja.</font>

109
00:09:25,260 --> 00:09:26,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak tahu aku sibuk.</font>

110
00:09:26,300 --> 00:09:29,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tampak sibuk, jadi aku
akan langsung ke intinya.</font>

111
00:09:29,230 --> 00:09:31,200
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalian yang diluar tidak bisa menghentikannya?</font>

112
00:09:31,200 --> 00:09:34,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Ratu ada di sini. Siapa pun
harus menunjukkan rasa hormat.</font>

113
00:09:39,240 --> 00:09:42,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau memberitahu kalau datang,
aku pasti akan bersiap-siap.</font>

114
00:09:42,810 --> 00:09:44,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan menyiapkan beberapa <i>wine</i>.</font>

115
00:09:44,280 --> 00:09:46,920
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini bukan hal mendesak jadi
tidak perlu aku memberitahumu dulu.</font>

116
00:09:47,180 --> 00:09:50,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau datang larut
malam begini padahal bukan hal mendesak?</font>

117
00:09:50,520 --> 00:09:53,320
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan menyelenggarakan perjamuan
untuk para utusan.</font>

118
00:09:54,090 --> 00:09:55,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Lakukan apapun yang kau mau.</font>

119
00:09:56,190 --> 00:09:58,690
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku perlu izin untuk melakukan persiapannya.</font>

120
00:09:58,690 --> 00:10:00,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Sejak kapan kau meminta izin dariku?</font>

121
00:10:01,160 --> 00:10:02,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu aku akan melakukannya.</font>

122
00:10:02,730 --> 00:10:04,300
<font color=#FFFF00>Lakukanlah.</font>

123
00:10:12,480 --> 00:10:14,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Raja selalu
peduli pada...</font>

124
00:10:14,640 --> 00:10:16,550
<font color=#FFFF00>...kesehatan Ratu.</font>

125
00:10:16,710 --> 00:10:19,150
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku memang tidak banyak tahu,</font>

126
00:10:19,150 --> 00:10:21,050
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi aku tahu beberapa obat.</font>

127
00:10:22,850 --> 00:10:24,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika anda mengizinkanku untuk memeriksa...</font>

128
00:10:24,550 --> 00:10:27,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kau tahu apa penyakitku,</font>

129
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:29,660
<font color=#FFFF00>...kau akan membuatkan obat untukku?</font>

130
00:10:29,660 --> 00:10:32,560
<font color=#FFFF00>Dengan seluruh usaha dan ilmuku,
aku akan...</font>

131
00:10:32,560 --> 00:10:33,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Nak.</font>

132
00:10:33,930 --> 00:10:34,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, Ratu.</font>

133
00:10:34,930 --> 00:10:36,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sangat buru-buru.</font>

134
00:10:36,900 --> 00:10:39,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pasti ingin meracuni obatku.</font>

135
00:10:40,770 --> 00:10:42,110
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak akan berani.</font>

136
00:10:43,170 --> 00:10:46,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita lihat dulu apa Raja akan
menjadikanmu selir.</font>

137
00:10:47,280 --> 00:10:50,080
<font color=#FFFF00>Dengan begitu kau baru bisa
bermimpi untuk meraih pergelangan kakiku.</font>

138
00:11:24,850 --> 00:11:26,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tahu bagaimana rasanya.</font>

139
00:11:27,980 --> 00:11:29,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf?</font>

140
00:11:29,750 --> 00:11:32,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana rasanya memiliki perasaan
yang tidak terbalas.</font>

141
00:11:34,890 --> 00:11:36,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Setiap hari,</font>

142
00:11:37,730 --> 00:11:39,830
<font color=#FFFF00>...hatimu akan terluka.</font>

143
00:11:42,570 --> 00:11:44,330
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sering melihatnya.</font>

144
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:56,650
<font color=#FFFF00>Mana yang lebih sulit?</font>

145
00:12:00,720 --> 00:12:02,120
<font color=#FFFF00>Untuk membuatnya tetap dekat...</font>

146
00:12:03,620 --> 00:12:06,360
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan membiarkan hatiku terluka setiap hari,</font>

147
00:12:06,620 --> 00:12:08,420
<font color=#FFFF00>...atau tidak melihatnya sama sekali?</font>

148
00:12:11,790 --> 00:12:13,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku berharap lupa.</font>

149
00:12:17,630 --> 00:12:18,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku hanya berharap.</font>

150
00:12:36,250 --> 00:12:38,920
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau yakin So Ah
ada di daftar persembahan?</font>

151
00:12:38,920 --> 00:12:40,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

152
00:12:40,090 --> 00:12:42,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Daftarnya sudah bersama para utusan.</font>

153
00:12:42,020 --> 00:12:43,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Kapan mereka akan pergi?</font>

154
00:12:43,430 --> 00:12:44,960
<font color=#FFFF00>36 jam lagi.</font>

155
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:46,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka akan berangkat pagi-pagi sekali.</font>

156
00:12:47,400 --> 00:12:49,970
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak ada waktu. Aku butuh Guru Lee.</font>

157
00:12:51,100 --> 00:12:52,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak menemukannya?</font>

158
00:12:52,370 --> 00:12:54,670
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ayolah./ Minumlah.</i></font>

159
00:12:54,670 --> 00:12:57,240
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Cepat./ Pelan-pelan.</i></font>

160
00:12:57,240 --> 00:13:00,240
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ini./ Ya ampun.</i></font>

161
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:02,150
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Minum, minum./ Tambah lagi.</i></font>

162
00:13:07,650 --> 00:13:09,250
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Sebentar lagi.</i></font>

163
00:13:09,250 --> 00:13:11,020
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ini supmu.</i></font>

164
00:13:11,020 --> 00:13:12,420
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Bawa kemari.</i></font>

165
00:13:13,660 --> 00:13:14,790
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Cepat.</i></font>

166
00:13:14,790 --> 00:13:16,960
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku akan antar. Aku akan antar.</i></font>

167
00:13:16,960 --> 00:13:18,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan kau.</font>

168
00:13:25,100 --> 00:13:28,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku melihatnya sendiri!</font>

169
00:13:28,740 --> 00:13:30,970
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tidak mungkin. Jangan bercanda.</i></font>

170
00:13:30,970 --> 00:13:33,510
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau pasti salah./
Percayalah padaku.</i></font>

171
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:48,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan menuangkan minuman untukmu.</font>

172
00:13:48,520 --> 00:13:50,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, aku akan menuangkan sendiri.</font>

173
00:13:50,990 --> 00:13:53,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu, apa yang akan aku lakukan?</font>

174
00:14:02,640 --> 00:14:04,210
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa tidak enak?</font>

175
00:14:04,210 --> 00:14:06,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia datang terlalu cepat.
Dia hanya mementingkan kepentingan sendiri.</font>

176
00:14:06,940 --> 00:14:07,940
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

177
00:14:10,550 --> 00:14:13,420
<font color=#FFFF00>Masih ada beberapa <i>wine</i> yang
belum aku minum.</font>

178
00:14:14,320 --> 00:14:16,650
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisakah aku minum masing-masing
seteguk?</font>

179
00:14:16,950 --> 00:14:19,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Utusan akan pergi satu hari lagi.</font>

180
00:14:19,790 --> 00:14:22,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita harus menemukan dokumen
Tuan Eun sebelum itu.</font>

181
00:14:22,760 --> 00:14:25,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Orang suruhanku sudah mencari-cari
di pinggiran Ibukota.</font>

182
00:14:25,260 --> 00:14:26,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika San dikirim sebelum...</font>

183
00:14:26,860 --> 00:14:30,100
<font color=#FFFF00>...kita membuat dia mentransfer hartanya,
maka semuanya akan menjadi rumit.</font>

184
00:15:00,530 --> 00:15:03,770
