<font color=#FFFF00>Sudah lama.</font>

267
00:20:16,250 --> 00:20:19,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mencintainya, bukan? Nona San.</font>

268
00:20:22,190 --> 00:20:24,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah tahu.</font>

269
00:20:26,090 --> 00:20:29,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Hati seseorang tidak bisa dilihat.
