284
00:21:23,080 --> 00:21:27,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Inilah aku, Orabeoni.</font>

285
00:21:40,600 --> 00:21:42,370
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau selalu seperti
ini saat kecil.</font>

286
00:21:43,200 --> 00:21:44,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Seperti apa?</font>

287
00:21:46,500 --> 00:21:48,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mengatakan sesuatu
