<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

302
00:22:53,600 --> 00:22:55,240
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Ini perintah Ratu.</i></font>

303
00:22:56,240 --> 00:22:58,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak akan menerima perintah Ratu.</font>

304
00:23:00,210 --> 00:23:03,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia membutuhkan bantuan saat
