310
00:23:59,170 --> 00:24:00,670
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku menemui So Ah tadi malam.</font>

311
00:24:03,570 --> 00:24:05,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pikir kau sedang dikurung.</font>

312
00:24:05,810 --> 00:24:08,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku kabur.
